        <div id="factions">
            <div id="horde">
                <p>The Horde, one of the two major factions in the World of Warcraft universe, is a diverse coalition of
                    races bound by a common goal: survival and dominance. Comprised of proud and resilient races such as
                    the brutish Orcs, noble Tauren, cunning Trolls, shrewd Forsaken, enigmatic Blood Elves, and
                    relentless Goblins, the Horde values strength, honor, and unity above all else. Originating from the
                    harsh lands of Draenor, they seek to carve out their destiny in the tumultuous world of Azeroth,
                    fiercely defending their territories while forging new alliances. With their steadfast determination
                    and unwavering loyalty, the Horde stands as a formidable force, ready to confront any challenge that
                    stands in their path.</p>

                <img src="sprites/horde.png" alt="Horde">
            </div>


            <div id="alliance">
                <img src="sprites/alliance.png" alt="Alliance">
                <p>The Alliance, a powerful coalition of races in the World of Warcraft realm, embodies unity,
                    diversity, and valor. Bringing together noble and diverse civilizations, the Alliance is an alliance
                    of humans, stalwart dwarves, enigmatic night elves, resilient gnomes, and righteous draenei. Formed
                    in the wake of great conflicts, including the First and Second Wars, the Alliance stands as a beacon
                    of hope and civilization against the chaos and darkness that threaten Azeroth. With a dedication to
                    justice, diplomacy, and the protection of all free peoples, the Alliance tirelessly defends its
                    realms, seeks peaceful coexistence, and strives for the greater good of all.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section id="races">
            <h2>Create your legend</h2>
